ive Perso-Arabic script along with standard Roman representations and morphological analysis. Written in an accessible style from a basic linguistic theory perspective, this work will be of use to linguistic researchers, language scholars, and students of the languages of Pakistan and South Asia.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 0aHindkō dialect. 0aPanjabi languagezPakistanzPāṭa. 0aPanjabi language. 0aSiraiki language. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh  aPakistani Punjabi.1 aConners, Thomas J., eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aHefright, Brook.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2019z978311071956708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDe Gruyter Mouton Contemporary 2016-2019z978311074297808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishz978311061076508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2019 Englishz978311061030708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2019z9783110606287oZDB-23-DSP0 cEPUBz97815015003290 cprintz978161451296740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978161451225740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781614512257423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781614512257.jpg  a978-3-11-061030-7  EBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-061076-5  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-071956-7  DG Plus eBook-Package 2019b2019  a978-3-11-074297-8  De Gruyter Mouton Contemporary 2016-2019c2016d2019  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  